    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wish of Hers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wish of Hers 是一款回合制俯视角动作 Roguelike 游戏，核心在于构筑与成长，在不断变化的不稳定梦境中生存下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一局游戏都围绕能力选择、词缀组合以及关键决策展开。通过不断尝试与优化，打造属于你的最强构筑。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高强度、快节奏的回合制战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着生存推进而不断扩展的程序生成地图</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人持续强化，挑战逐步升级</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/extras/11dcdd6c83f12dfee7c9d55c8dee490a.poster.avif?t=1768580880\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/extras/11dcdd6c83f12dfee7c9d55c8dee490a.webm?t=1768580880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/extras/11dcdd6c83f12dfee7c9d55c8dee490a.mp4?t=1768580880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Your Run</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过 Dream Condensers 解锁并升级能力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用 Aspects 深度改造能力，形成强力联动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借助 Reality Shaper，将最多 4 个词缀自由组合到单个能力上</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构筑自由度高，每一局玩法差异明显</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/extras/29a5c28d86674eb5507dd9cdc795335d.poster.avif?t=1768580880\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/extras/29a5c28d86674eb5507dd9cdc795335d.webm?t=1768580880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/extras/29a5c28d86674eb5507dd9cdc795335d.mp4?t=1768580880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Progression &amp; Choice</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单局内升级核心属性，形成成长曲线</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有限的属性槽带来策略取舍</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战与奖励会根据你的选择产生变化</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/extras/931122c9a7d0448fcb4b476be9d6b841.poster.avif?t=1768580880\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/extras/931122c9a7d0448fcb4b476be9d6b841.webm?t=1768580880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/extras/931122c9a7d0448fcb4b476be9d6b841.mp4?t=1768580880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Current State</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当前 Demo 展示了游戏的核心系统与玩法方向。<br>未来的抢先体验版本将加入更多能力、角色、多层地图、Boss 与改变流程的关键事件。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Future</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185880/extras/0da7cff068245e3527cd149d3a1b8c6e.avif?t=1768580880\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
